I’m going to kick your ass when I get
out of this, you pointy head fuck!
insect. I will attend to you shortly.
Oooooo scary! I don’t care anymore.
Already in Hell, so maybe I’ll get my kicks

cries of pain will hasten his steps.
What in the pit are you doing here?!
Asha?! Thank god, I’m so glad to see you.
You gotta help me get my friend out of here!
With the two of us, we can take Orgoluuk.
Are you mad? We cannot fight him, especially in this place!
This is Orgoluuk’s territory in Hell, meaning he has
enhanced power while residing in it.
Can’t we just slow down time, run in there,
grab Sabrina, and take us back to Earth?
His domain, his rules. That is how it works down here for
high demons. There are old spells carved into these walls
Even IF we were to flee to another level of The Underworld,
I am not entirely certain if I could get you back home.

someone like me. Why do you think Orgoluuk needed to be
